item.title: Homework 0: Metacircular Interpreter Implementation
item.description:
Link to Homework 0

Do your homework by forking the Github repo for the project into a private branch. You may collaborate with a group of as many students (in the class) as you like. If multiple students collaborate, all of their names must be signed on the project, and you must also email me (Kris) a rough breakdown of what each participant did.
